{"tid":264871,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"乜嘢叫【識著衫】？","createTime":"2017-05-31T07:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T08:36:42.000Z","uid":61443,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a4ee133d2247774491f5234753d48f7703daa8","tid":264871,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"首先我自己都係亂著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說<br />\n我有個女仔fd<br />\n唔靚唔特別好普通<br />\n同過佢買衫<br />\n心諗過你揀左呢件衫點搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次同佢出街<br />\n佢就係著返件衫<br />\n發現佢著得好好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係加啲減啲咁<br />\n仲有覺得個style襯佢個性格 <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢著完唔係識飛同想J <br />\n但係咁樣得佢諗到同襯佢個性格 <br />\n同埋令到佢自己好睇左<br />\n<br />\n可能咁樣先叫【識著衫】掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69493d72ab35c17d45127de43e4f4b2c893cfd3b","tid":264871,"uid":58666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"識得取長補短囉"},{"pid":"040c3df7dd7946f6d4f8f35606a715402a5da03f","tid":264871,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48893cd6ac8d83dc7051250d6486ccd399316fe4","tid":264871,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n返小學學中文啦"},{"pid":"db7e340014fb0ba77b1869f11aac7754d97a0895","tid":264871,"uid":42170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母<br />\n返小學學中文啦</blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1撚999"},{"pid":"6ac48f56f7cb29a3246ad5d01b3cb566cd6696f6","tid":264871,"uid":114993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"圖都冇好難參與討論"},{"pid":"9684ff8e7df49f2bb87573a0b86f0082ba289a03","tid":264871,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"